text: Eduardo Higareda (born 26 February 1937) is a Mexican equestrian. He competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics, the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1971 Pan American Games Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City
